## 4. Integrations
Trim Boss connects with **Google Sheets** and **n8n** for workflow automation. Use of these services is subject to their respective terms and privacy policies.

## 5. Data Handling
Trim Boss transmits user-supplied data solely for executing requested automations. It does not independently collect, retain, or resell data.

